=== Hiragana character ===
'''を''' (''wo'')

For a list of words starting with this hiragana see: [[Wiktionary:Japanese index を]]
====Alternative forms====
*[[ヲ]] (''wo'') - katakana (rare)


===Particle===
[[Category:Japanese particles]]
'''を''' (''o'')

# (''particle'')
#: Grammatical marker following the direct object. When used in this sense it is almost always pronounced "o" instead of "wo".
#* [[本]]'''を'''[[読む]]
#*: [[ほん]]'''を'''[[よむ]]
#*: ''[[hon]] '''o''' [[yomu]]''
#*: to [[read]] a [[book]]

